reviewText: Glad to finally own this.  Love this anime, pretty good rom-com.  Streaming can bite me, I like owning disc still.
Sooo freaking cute!!! And there is a lot of humor as wellif you like romance, give this a try
It came in great condition and a timely manner.  It just wasn't what I expected.  Had a hard time watching felt it was really slow.
Fave series. Durable slip cover. Love the "study book" too, plus its hardcover. This is now my treasured possession.
